      <h2>Les 4 chiffres qui font mouche en réunion.</h2>

      <div class="args">
        <article class="arg">
          <div class="big">18<span class="u">%</span>
</div>
          <div class="ttl">des communes respectent les seuils EGalim.</div>
          <div class="src">AMF · 2024</div>
        </article>
        <article class="arg">
          <div class="big">8<span class="u">/10</span>
